snippet.title: One Direction - Night Changes (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
One Direction - Night Changes
Stream/Download:

(Lyrics):
[Verse 1: Zayn & Liam]
Goin' out tonight, changes into somethin' red
Her mother doesn't like that kind of dress
Everything she never had, she's showin' off
Drivin' too fast, moon is breakin' through her hair
She's headin' for somethin' that she won't forget
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

[Chorus: All & Harry]
(Ooh) We're only gettin' older, baby
(Ooh) And I've been thinkin' about it lately
(Ooh) Does it ever drive you crazy
(Ah-ah-ah) Just how fast the night changes?
(Ooh) Everything that you've ever dreamed of
(Ooh) Disappearin' when you wake up
(Ooh) But there's nothin' to be afraid of
(Ah-ah-ah) Even when the night changes
(Ooh) It will never change me and you

[Verse 2: Louis & Niall]
Chasin' her tonight, doubts are runnin' round her head
He's waitin', hides behind a cigarette
Heart is beatin' loud and she doesn't want it to stop
Movin' too fast, moon is lightin' up her skin
She's fallin', doesn't even know it yet
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

The Weeknd & Playboi Carti
[Chorus: All & Harry]
(Ooh) We're only gettin' older, baby
(Ooh) And I've been thinkin' about it lately
(Ooh) Does it ever drive you crazy
(Ah-ah-ah) Just how fast the night changes?
(Ooh) Everything that you've ever dreamed of
(Ooh) Disappearin' when you wake up
(Ooh) But there's nothin' to be afraid of
(Ah-ah-ah) Even when the night changes
(Ooh) It will never change me and you

[Post-Chorus: Liam]
Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh
Ooh, ooh, ooh
Ooh

Goin' out tonight, changes into somethin' red
Her mother doesn't like that kind of dress
Reminds her of the missin' piece of innocence she lost

snippet.title: Stranger Things 5 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
At long last‚Ä¶ we can begin. The trailer for the epic final season of STRANGER THINGS is here.

VOL 1 - November 26, 5pm PT
VOL 2 - Christmas, 5pm PT
THE FINALE - New Year‚Äôs Eve, 5pm PT

*releasing worldwide all at once, date may vary based on your local timezone

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81297917

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Stranger Things 5 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

With Hawkins under lockdown, El in hiding and danger lurking at every turn, the entire party unites with a single goal: to hunt and kill Vecna.

snippet.title: Ikkis - Official Trailer | Dharmendra | Agastya | Jaideep | Simar | Sriram R | Dinesh V | This Dec
snippet.description:

Dinesh Vijan and Maddock Films present #Ikkis, a true untold story of India‚Äôs youngest Param Vir Chakra awardee - Second Lieutenant Arun Khetarpal directed by Sriram Raghavan.

#IkkisTrailer Out Now!

Share your #QissaAtIkkis because every legendary story starts young.

In cinemas December 2025!

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Release Trailer 2 (Hindi) | Prabhas, Rana | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

Worldwide Releasing On Oct 31st 2025.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad 
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov
Dance Choreographers: Prem Rakshit, Shankar, Dinesh Kumar, Jani
Editor: Tammiraju 
Costume Designer: Rama Rajamouli, Prashanti Tripirneni 
Dialogues:
Telugu - C.H. Vijay Kumar, Ajay Kumar G
Hindi - Manoj Muntashir
Tamil - Karky
DI & Sound Mix: Annapurna  Studios
Marketing: Walls & Trends


Follow us on: 
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/BaahubaliMovie
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Baahubalimovie
Instagram - http://instagram.com/baahubalimovie
Pinterest - http://www.pinterest.com/baahubalimovie/
Tumblr - http://baahubalimovie.tumblr.com/

Note: If you wish to share this video, please make sure you embed the link and share the original source. Please avoid other methods of copying or duplicating the video, and help us support anti-piracy measures in any way you can. Thank you - Baahubali Team

snippet.title: SACAR aka Lil Buddha - Feels Good ft. Ninja YNL (2025 Version) (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Lil Buddha on Instagram -   https://instagram.com/younglion888 

Ecstasy In The Palace available at - https://trap.li/ecstasy

Music Video by Lil Buddha, Ninja and Starboi Virgin performing Feels Good from the deluxe version of the album "Ecstasy In The Palace".

Produced by Jxxded.

Recorded by Spark at OMG.

Mixed by Jxxded.

Directed by Thomas GM.

Costumes Designed by Tsabinz.

Ninja Styled by iamken. 

Jxxded on Instagram - https://instagram.com/jxxded  

Ninja on Instagram - https://instagram.com/ninjaynl  

Starboi Virgin on Instagram - https://instagram.com/ghxstboy888  

Thomas GM on Instagram - https://instagram.com/th0mx.gm

Tsabinz on Instagram - https://instagram.com/tsabinz

Lil Noto on Instagram - https://instagram.com/noto4l  

HYPE on Instagram - https://instagram.com/beatsbyhype  

psykid on Instagram - https://instagram.com/thispsykidmakesmusic_  

Spark (OMG) on Instagram - https://instagram.com/omg.spark  

Lyrics

Lil Buddha aka Young Lion

Yeah yeah yeah yeah
Lil Buddha
Ecstasy In The Palace
I'd just like to thank god
For this beautiful life that we get to live
Man 
This beautiful music that we get to make
It's so surreal
Yo

I ain't always had a life like this 
Baby I had to fight for this
Ask the reason why I write verses 
It's for the tens of millions that i might possess 
If I just make it 
So let me bake then you taste it 
My crew and I on the track feel amazing 
As we get on the cooking 
It's looking like we gonna get a lot of show bookings from KTM to Brooklyn 
The hardships I was faced with got me money chasing
I don't wanna leave my youth just wasted 
I wanna make that billion dollars 
And I'm losing my patience 
So I snatch the crown with no hesitation 
I'm just making a point 
Sing and rap and put the nation on the map 
Yo Imma give it validation 
Worked so hard now i earn the guap 
Sitting on the top easy life on that permanent vacation 
These melodies 
I ain't hearing what they telling me 
Ain't nobody getting me and it's killing me 
But I'm feeling the beat that he bringing 
It's my remedy 
Killing it no felony
Feels good doesn't it

Ninja

I only show off when the shows on right 
We about to blow up soon you better hold on tight 
I always show up my crew we glow up light like fluorescent
We shine like ornaments cook our own don't order it 
On the mic I'm sorcerous
They can't handle my morbidness 
Lyrically torturous to emcees I can't afford to miss 
I'm in a killing spree Danny Barbosa 
Hitman sipping wine 
Chilling at Mendoza
Focused on real bread unlike you loafers 
I went rogue to burn your fucking hope like a toaster 
Never had no faith in me remember what I told ya
I went past the snakes now I'm alone king cobra
Ooh
Now it's cobra strikes when I hold the mic
Take you on a roller coaster ride with the flows I write
I need more in my life I got dough on my mind 
Ready to take off feel like I'm on the borderline

Starboi Virgin

Sipping on that youth water
Tryna living it up
If she looks hotter
Imma give it to her
Feeling good 
Smoking Hollywood
Light it up get higher boo
Feeling good 
Smoking Hollywood
Light it up get higher boo
Yeah it feels good
Yeah it feels good

Lil Buddha aka Young Lion

I mean this music that I feel in my soul I know it's infinite
I thank god for what I was gifted with 
And Imma make sure I use it for good 
Take my family out of the hood 
Cause if I don't recognize in time what I have 
Spend my time with the lads and don't focus on my raps
I know that Imma look back 
Regret the money that I could've stacked
I'm good at that
Nobody got the vision that Lil Buddha got 
On my momma on god Imma do this 
And to the haters I swear that I'm the rudest 
Trynna travel the world through this
Trynna break the family curse through this 
Fill my momma purse through this
And through this verse I disperse all the judging words 
Bitches chirp but you know I'm busy stacking birds
It's a shame if you ain't still heard my name
From the heart yeah you know I got the flame

Starboi Virgin

Sipping on that youth water
Tryna living it up
If she looks hotter
Imma give it to her
Feeling good

We are celebrating your comments for the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video. Thank you for supporting CCR! 

Watch the official Have You Ever Seen The Rain music video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u1V8YRJnr4Q

Follow Creedence Clearwater Revival:
https://www.youtube.com/@TheOfficialCCR
https://instagram.com/theofficialccr
https://tiktok.com/@theofficialccr
https://facebook.com/ccr
https://twitter.com/theofficialccr

Listen to ‚ÄúCCR: Chronicle - The 20 Greatest Hits‚Äù: https://ffm.to/ccr-chronicle

Visit the CCR store:
https://ccr.concord.com/products/

Subscribe to the CCR Newsletter: https://manage.kmail-lists.com/subscriptions/subscribe?a=Ut6Y6V&g=WyE6eZ

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom‚ÄØFogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of‚ÄØthe day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.‚ÄØ‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 ‚Äì 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They‚Äôve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like ‚ÄúBad Moon Rising,‚Äù ‚ÄúDown on the Corner,‚Äù ‚ÄúFortunate Son,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave You Ever Seen the Rain,‚Äù ‚ÄúProud Mary,‚Äù ‚ÄúBorn on the Bayou,‚Äù ‚ÄúTravelin‚Äô Band‚Äù and ‚ÄúUp Around the Bend‚Äù have been ingrained into pop culture ‚Äî not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America‚Äôs greatest rock ‚Äôn‚Äô roll band.

#ccr #creedenceclearwaterrevival #haveyoueverseentherain

snippet.title: NEW LEOPARD REWORK IN BLOX FRUITS!
snippet.description:
Today I reacted to the new leopard rework showcase. Make sure you watch the whole video to find out what happens. 

FOLTYN MERCH: https://foltyn.shop/

--Socials--

Discord: https://discord.gg/hqwZhrkqRr

Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/1177555...

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/foltynn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.description:
The third day of the Season 16 Playoffs begins! Today, one team will be selected to represent Indonesia at the M7 World Championship, while another team will be eliminated, forced to bury their dream of competing on the international stage! A peak performance is required to prove they are worthy of representing Indonesia and advancing to the next round. Who will prevail in the Upper Bracket Finals and who will fall in the Lower Bracket Semifinals? Keep watching the MPL ID Season 16 Playoffs and don't miss the excitement!üî•

snippet.title: The Clashteroid - A Hammer Jam Film
snippet.description:
Builder got his hands on a mysterious Meteorite Hammer sent by  @hankschannel ! For the entire Hammer Jam event, Home Village upgrade costs and timers are cut in half, and Resource Collectors produce 2x faster with double capacity. Brace for impact, Chief!

Follow us on our Socials!

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Ujan Shakya - Baby (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
MEY STUDIO & VISIONS MEDIA PRODUCTION
PRESENTS

BABY by Ujan Shakya || New Newari Song || New Nepal Bhasa Song || New Nepali Song

"Baby" explores the theme of love. It depicts the concept of love at first sight through a narrative that combines imagination and emotion. The piece is characterized as an emotional afrobeat , featuring a blend of Newari instruments.
